# General optimization tips

This project uses Astro as a framework, and also Solid to load certain javascript elements

- Use Astro optimizations wherever possible, for example using custom tags, actions, etc.# Styling
- Use tailwindcss as much as possible for styling, if it's possible to avoid using CSS through tailwind then use tailwind

# Image optimizations

- use `<Image>`, an astro component, instead of `<img>`
- When importing icons (svg), attempt using iconify through unplugin-icons if possible
